Torin/Fury/Devilcat::

Devilcat is there waiting when Noir arrives; Torin and Fury get there 
soon after.  Fury is literally hopping up and down in his impatience 
to be doing something.

"Well, that's three," Devilcat says.  "We'll probably have to wait a 
bit for the others."

> -- Noir --
>

considers
